<div style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #dc2626; margin-bottom: 20px;">Account Deletion Requested</h1>

  <p>Hi <%= @user.email %>,</p>

  <p>Your account deletion has been requested and is scheduled to be processed.</p>

  <p><strong>If you did not request this</strong>, please contact support immediately to cancel the deletion.</p>

  <p><strong>If you did request this</strong>, your account and all associated data will be permanently deleted. This action cannot be undone.</p>

  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
    This is a security notification and cannot be disabled.
  </p>
</div>
